{"tid":1686161,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"琴晚老蘭單野真係港豬都變黃絲","createTime":"2019-11-01T03:11:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T03:29:26.000Z","uid":264319,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"30d6357540855f2b26d27febf731f8dba2d2a932","tid":1686161,"uid":264319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T03:11:32.000Z","msg":"認真<br />\n身邊好幾個去玩開既港豬琴晚都有落老蘭<br />\n好不滿表示警察搞到佢哋出去玩<br />\n鬧警察鬧到飛起<br />\n之後話係咪想搞到全香港人都憎警察先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實警察們你地有無腦？<br />\n去得老蘭大部分都係去玩/蒲開<br />\n你地咪即係此地無銀三百兩<br />\n話俾人聽你地得閒無野做要濫捕人<br />\n然後得罪一班本身對你地無咩敵意/中立既人<br />\n唉 呢D咪豬隊友<br />\n仲覺得沾沾自喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7a4c1d7ce075e111c9253f1db148ac22e218258","tid":1686161,"uid":221360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T03:21:47.000Z","msg":"【突發】11月2活動需要大量文宣，你我都做到<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/erxDAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/erxDAS</a>"},{"pid":"b8ad7dbaf54d5bed2fffc390b4378ae50348ad5c","tid":1686161,"uid":14605,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T03:25:01.000Z","msg":"呢d通常嬲2日會變返藍絲，唔駛擔心"},{"pid":"63a36024a3f27a0d218ff58b6230b766a553c46d","tid":1686161,"uid":186844,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T03:29:26.000Z","msg":"黑警根本唔會理你嬲唔嬲佢 拉左先講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}